@startuml live-logging-architecture
!include _standard-style.puml
title Live Logging System Architecture

component [User] 
component [Claude]
component [Tools]
component [Transcript Files]

component [Status Line]
component [Transcript Analyzer] 

component [Groq AI]
component [Session Database]

component [Live Session Files]

[User] --> [Claude] : requests
[Claude] --> [Tools] : executes  
[Tools] --> [Transcript Files] : writes JSONL

[Status Line] --> [Transcript Analyzer] : quick analysis
[Transcript Files] --> [Transcript Analyzer] : reads

[Transcript Analyzer] --> [Groq AI] : background analysis
[Groq AI] --> [Session Database] : saves insights
[Session Database] --> [Live Session Files] : real-time logs

[Transcript Analyzer] --> [Status Line] : session info

note bottom
Key Features:
- Under 10ms status updates
- Background AI analysis  
- Real-time session files
- No hooks required
end note

@enduml